
## 📝 How to Run
1. Install libraries and ESP32 board support.
2. Upload `people_counter.ino` to ESP32.
3. Change SSID, password, and ThingSpeak API key in code.
4. Power the system and observe LCD + light control.
5. Monitor real-time data on ThingSpeak dashboard.

